STATE of Iowa, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Donovan Mason EDWARDS, Defendant-Appellant. No. 17-2007 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed January 9, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Donovan Edwards appeals his criminal conviction following the denial of his motion for a new trial. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
